      "title": "Germinal centres: role in B-cell physiology and malignancy",
      "abstract": "Germinal centres are the main source of memory B cells and plasma cells that produce high-affinity antibodies in the body. In this Review, Ulf Klein and Riccardo Dalla-Favera describe the relationship between the cellular and molecular dynamics of germinal centres and the pathogenesis of B-cell lymphomas."
